      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered with hand-washes every weekend. It looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you\u2019ve been looking for that perfect, 'like-new' ride without the dealership stress, this is definitely the one. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have\u2014come take a look and see for yourself!",
