    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing surgical mechanical precision. The S54 3.2L inline-six remains a masterpiece of atmospheric engineering, featuring individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. This example boasts a factory Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a perfectly calibrated M Variable Differential Lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral G-loads. The suspension geometry is factory-spec, providing the telepathic feedback these chassis are renowned for. A truly pristine, collector-quality specimen for the discerning purist.",
